Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1200
Set Height 600
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 100ms

Type "zen find France" Enter
Sleep 2s

Type "rust" Sleep 300ms
Sleep 1s

Backspace 4
Sleep 500ms

Type "capital" Sleep 300ms
Sleep 1s

Down
Sleep 500ms

Up
Sleep 500ms

Escape
Sleep 1s
